    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Note from developer:</h2>Hey friends! If yall end up loving Princess Pyro, I could certainly see a more elaborate continuation or derivative in the future. Thank you SO much for your support. Please enjoy and have fun &lt;3<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/ff4d3a2f8ef38648a69e53430d350a89.poster.avif?t=1650498374\" width=600 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/ff4d3a2f8ef38648a69e53430d350a89.webm?t=1650498374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/ff4d3a2f8ef38648a69e53430d350a89.mp4?t=1650498374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Princess Pyro's searing fire powers are the only hope to revert the mysteriously sudden nightfall and fight back the encroaching forces of darkness!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/302fc750f7658e034e8d5f8a7d41a7d5.poster.avif?t=1650498374\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/302fc750f7658e034e8d5f8a7d41a7d5.webm?t=1650498374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/302fc750f7658e034e8d5f8a7d41a7d5.mp4?t=1650498374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GAME</h2>A short and sweet nod to retro arcade gaming, with some roguelike difficulty, and metroidvania flourishes! Unleash fiery havoc across Pyro Castle to uncover the source of the sudden nightfall! Fight your way to the end and defeat the source of darkness... Dun dun dunnnnn. Rack up points to get on the score board.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/7447e22cd4419626dfab360733881395.poster.avif?t=1650498374\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/7447e22cd4419626dfab360733881395.webm?t=1650498374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/7447e22cd4419626dfab360733881395.mp4?t=1650498374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE MAKING</h2>Princess Pyro was made with a lot of soul and aimed for that flashy arcade style with roguelike difficulty.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/a17542de40daf35e608a003e8a10f4f2.poster.avif?t=1650498374\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/a17542de40daf35e608a003e8a10f4f2.webm?t=1650498374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/a17542de40daf35e608a003e8a10f4f2.mp4?t=1650498374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREDITS</h2>Creative commons music by Sound Forces. A bit of inspiration from games like Rogue Legacy and Metroid Dread.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/76d04923f83c99c39475ec6efa450b43.poster.avif?t=1650498374\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/76d04923f83c99c39475ec6efa450b43.webm?t=1650498374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/76d04923f83c99c39475ec6efa450b43.mp4?t=1650498374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXTRAS &amp; NOTES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/fa38ff738bf3abd06537be0e42b396ac.poster.avif?t=1650498374\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/fa38ff738bf3abd06537be0e42b396ac.webm?t=1650498374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/fa38ff738bf3abd06537be0e42b396ac.mp4?t=1650498374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Xinput controllers supported.<br></li><li> Three difficulty modes.<br></li><li> Female protagonist.<br></li><li> Locally saved hi-scores (like an old arcade box).<br></li><li> Secret spots and optional precision-jumps.<br></li><li> An in-hiding Ms Goblets.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/64accbd8d033f63fd173348335910c52.poster.avif?t=1650498374\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/64accbd8d033f63fd173348335910c52.webm?t=1650498374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/64accbd8d033f63fd173348335910c52.mp4?t=1650498374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Please enjoy and have fun &lt;3<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/394cd6f8cb2d5810226645fddb893070.apng?t=1650498374\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903690/extras/394cd6f8cb2d5810226645fddb893070.poster.avif?t=1650498374\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=45 /></picture></span>",
